// views/partials/step_generalInfo.pug
div#import-general-info.buckets-guide-container
  // ───────── Title & intro ─────────
  h2 📄 Get Your Spreadsheet Ready
  p Before importing your <strong>Account</strong> data, make sure your spreadsheet includes the following columns (✅ required / ⚙️ optional):

  // ───────── Checklist ─────────
  ol.guide-steps
    li
      span.step-icon 1️⃣
      span.step-text
        strong Client ID (⚙️ Optional, but recommended)
        |  – Unique identifier for each client
    li
      span.step-icon 2️⃣
      span.step-text
        strong Account Number (✅)
        |  – Unique account identifier
    li
      span.step-icon 3️⃣
      span.step-text
        strong Account Value (⚙️)
        |  – Current total value
    li
      span.step-icon 4️⃣
      span.step-text
        strong Account Type (⚙️)
        |  – e.g. IRA, 401(k), Trust
    li
      span.step-icon 5️⃣
      span.step-text
        strong Custodian (⚙️)
        |  – Financial institution holding the account
    li
      span.step-icon 6️⃣
      span.step-text
        strong Tax Status (⚙️)
        |  – e.g. Taxable, Tax-Deferred, Tax-Free

  // ───────── Best‑practice tips ─────────
  p.mt-3
    | • Keep Client IDs / Account Numbers consistent for future uploads.  
    br
    | • Source data from any CRM, or start with our template below.

  // ───────── Download + Learn‑More links ─────────
  a.import-action-item.d-block.mt-2(href='/downloads/general-account-import-template.xlsx' download)
    i.fas.fa-file-download.me-1
    | Download the Account Import template
  a.import-action-item.learn-more-btn.d-block.mt-2(      
    href='#'
    data-video-id='76979871'                           
    data-bs-toggle='modal'
    data-bs-target='#learnMoreVideoModal'
  )
    i.fas.fa-play-circle.me-1
    | Watch an instructional video (2 min)
  

  // ───────── Example header row (optional) ─────────
  .example-header.mt-4
    h4 🧪 Example Header Row:
    code Client ID | Account Number | Account Value | Account Type | Custodian | Tax Status

